title: Coffee consumption in the U.S. 2013/14 - 2018/19
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags. In total the number of data points it has is 6.
Overall Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags has increased over the Year.

Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags is roughly constant from 2013/2014 to 2014/2015, slightly increasing from 2014/2015 to 2015/2016, roughly constant from 2015/2016 to 2016/2017, and lastly slightly increasing from 2016/2017 to 2018/2019.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014/2015 and 2015/2016.
Maximum Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags, about 26.5 was reported at Year 2018/2019
Minimum Consumption in million 60-kilogram bags about 23.58 was reached at Year 2014/2015
